{"tid":2291694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高等法院周家明：市民對警察提出私人檢控，明顯有一定重要性","createTime":"2020-11-19T03:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T04:21:34.000Z","uid":138409,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7ecffa1ad78c04aff12e5d8e52232c91e4374c","tid":2291694,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/3493308187449107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdInDisguise%2Fposts%2F3493308187449107&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5g1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=f3cb2107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/3493308187449107</a><br />\n周家明法官同時順道提到，就落實政府調查警暴的積極責任而言，容許市民提出私人檢控明顯有一定重要性<br />\n'94. Further, in order to give full force and effect to the rights protected by BOR 3, victims of police ill-treatment should be entitled to reasonable identification of the police officers concerned so that they may themselves commence civil actions or <span class=\"gold\">private prosecutions against the officers.</span> ...<br />\n'96. The existence of an effective system which allows identification of police officers who may have committed acts in violation of BOR 3 is integral to an effective system of investigation, and is essential to achieve the purpose of ensuring accountability for ill-treatment by police officers.  It also enables victims of police ill-treatment to start civil actions and <span class=\"gold\">private prosecutions against the police officers concerned</span>. ...'<br />\n<br />\n法庭判詞<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/HCAL001747_2019.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fen%2F2019%2FHCAL001747_2019.doc&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5g1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=d1732d20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/HCAL001747_2019.doc</a>"},{"pid":"67bb5bf0b7116cdcca51762c8d231f45f4898885","tid":2291694,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c77c7fad0a9ec284990b9e04c0325c7f3ea7aa90","tid":2291694,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:29:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"44f94406ce35c7aa5f6b1397b0d7e9f98a968f34","tid":2291694,"uid":43062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"律政司不斷撤回私人檢控<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269e24117be5472fbbecf1f3de94fd86a09cc91a","tid":2291694,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a514f7b672b4fb0cb360ece3738f5cbabde02232","tid":2291694,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d30cd194495738c3151d3b5034458bcc72dfc34","tid":2291694,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"你有你燒錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />律政司會幫你接手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400315e3c738bb01e7f647acebe46228204c4ff5","tid":2291694,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:53:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7be6bef26a278954b0fcba065aa9b9e9e227cefc","tid":2291694,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"2020仲容許?"},{"pid":"7787a143d1c864194acd798ad0492a9d3e63fa5f","tid":22916